strings: <voice_0x01001307><se_low>awesome: In the morning, good morning, rose found the garden.
<voice_0x01001308><se_low>awesome: The temperature and humidity in this cave is perfect for them. This is the only place where you can grow weeds in a corner.
<voice_0x01001309><se_low>awesome: Behind those bars is the ruins I'm talking about. They are mostly there.
<voice_0x0100130A><se_low>awesome: This place is something special. Therefore, we are unable to accommodate guests. I am very sorry.
